            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="serrasE" start="4372.737" end="x">. . . that she should be . . . 'killed alive,' that is, she should be burned alive, she should be conscious of her death.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="4380.847" end="x">Yes . . .</span>
