                <span class="">Edith Serras</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="serrasE" start="x" end="x">One sister was sick. And her sister had to be hanged that day.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="x" end="x">Yes . . .</span>
