            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Edith Serras</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="serrasE" start="x" end="x">And when the six girls were hanged—the large <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> had to look on at how they were being led to the 'guillotine' [the interview took place in France].</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="x" end="x">You mean the 'gallows?'</span>
        </li>
